OL,3,CKelso man says vulnerable people could
OL,4,Cbe cut off by changes to household
OL,5,Cenergy
OL,7,FA Scottish Borders man who experienced
OL,8,Fa year of difficulties trying to swap
OL,9,Fhis electricity meter says vulnerable
OL,10,Fpeople could be cut off by changes to
OL,11,Fhousehold energy.
OL,13,FMore than 300,000 UK households could
OL,14,Flose hot water and heating when Radio
OL,15,FTeleswitch Service (RTS) meters are
OL,16,Fswitched off at the end of June. The
OL,17,Fsystem uses radio signals to switch
OL,18,Fbetween peak and off-peak energy rates.
