OL,3,CKelso man says vulnerable people could
OL,4,Cbe cut off by changes to household
OL,5,Cenergy
OL,7,FIndustry regulator Ofgem has said the
OL,8,Frisks associated with not having a
OL,9,Ffunctioning meter include heating and
OL,10,Fhot water left continually on or off,
OL,11,Felectric storage heaters charging at
OL,12,Fthe wrong time of day, possibly
OL,13,Fleading to higher bills, and the
OL,14,Fsupplier being unable to confirm
OL,15,Felectricity usage during peak or off-
OL,16,Fpeak times.
OL,18,FThe UK Government says the service is
OL,19,Fstopping because the technology
OL,20,Funderpinning it is reaching the end of
OL,21,Fits operational life.
