OL,3,CKelso man says vulnerable people could
OL,4,Cbe cut off by changes to household
OL,5,Cenergy
OL,7,FThe charity Advice Direct Scotland
OL,8,Fhelped David Ashton, from Kelso, with
OL,9,Finstalling a smart meter after he
OL,10,Fexperienced a "very stressful" year of
OL,11,Ftrying to change his old system.
OL,13,FDavid had to wait for a specific
OL,14,Fcomponent after his energy provider
OL,15,Fwas initially unable to install a
OL,16,Fcompatible meter.
