OL,3,CKelso man says vulnerable people could
OL,4,Cbe cut off by changes to household
OL,5,Cenergy
OL,7,FHe said: "I use the computer a lot and
OL,8,FI'm researching it all, and I realised
OL,9,Fthat the end date was the end of June,
OL,10,Fwhich is coming up really quickly, and
OL,11,Fwe didn't want to be without central
OL,12,Fheating for the winter, and certainly
OL,13,Fwithout hot water.
OL,15,F"Or even the opposite, with it
OL,16,Fswitched on all the time. We don't
OL,17,Fwant that because it will increase our
OL,18,Fenergy bills."
