OL,3,CKelso man says vulnerable people could
OL,4,Cbe cut off by changes to household
OL,5,Cenergy
OL,7,FSpeaking about the deadline to upgrade
OL,8,Fhome meters by 30 June 2025, he added:
OL,9,F"It's almost like armageddon, disabled
OL,10,Fpeople, the poorest people, the ones
OL,11,Fwho are going to be hardest hit by
OL,12,Fthese changes, are going to be left
OL,13,Fwith either no heating and hot water,
OL,14,For it's all going to go on the same
OL,15,Fbill, which is going to be through the
OL,16,Froof."
