OL,3,CKelso man says vulnerable people could
OL,4,Cbe cut off by changes to household
OL,5,Cenergy
OL,7,FEnergy UK says more than 400,000 RTS
OL,8,Fmeters were still active across the UK
OL,9,F- with 130,000 in Scotland - in early
OL,10,FApril 2025. Energy companies are
OL,11,Fswitching around 40,000 meters each
OL,12,Fmonth.
OL,14,F5,011 meters still hadn't been
OL,15,Freplaced in the Scottish Borders,
OL,16,F6,371 in Dumfries and Galloway, and at
OL,17,Fleast 3,139 in Cumbria.
