OL,7,FNed Hammond, Energy UK's Deputy
OL,8,FDirector for Customers, said it wasn't
OL,9,F"completely impossible" but admitted
OL,10,Fit will be "very challenging" to
OL,11,Fswitch all meters by the deadline.
OL,13,FIf you live in England or Wales, you
OL,14,Fcan contact Citizens Advice for free
OL,15,Fand impartial advice about your energy
OL,16,Fsupply.
OL,18,FIf you live in Scotland, you can get
OL,19,Fadvice and information on
OL,20,Fenergyadvice.scot.
